headline: Nebius Tavily Deal Links AI Agents To Growing Cloud Infrastructure
summary: Nebius Group (NasdaqGS:NBIS) has acquired Tavily, a provider of agentic search software for AI agents in financial trading and coding. The company is expanding its AI infrastructure and data center footprint to support growing demand from enterprise customers. Nebius is backed by large contracts with major technology firms, including Meta and Microsoft, as it scales its AI cloud platform.
